com.galou.moodtracker.models

Class Mood

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.galou.moodtracker.models.Mood
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Mood
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Represents a Mood.

    A Mood is characterize by the following information:

    • a mood id corresponding to a drawable
    • a color
    • an object Date
    • a comment

    Implement the interface Serializable

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    galou
    See Also:
    MoodBank, Serialized Form
